While working with docker based microservices its very difficult to manually setup hundreds of microservice,
so docker compose is a tool using which we can describe about microservices in YAML file and quickly setup complete environment
with a single command
------------------
Compose is a tool for defining and running multi-container Docker applications. With Compose, you use a YAML file to configure your applicationâ€™s services. 
Then, with a single command, you create and start all the services from your configuration.
----------------------
Install Compose on Linux systems
wget https://github.com/vijaybirru/docker-compose.git
sudo curl -L "https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/download/1.23.2/docker-compose-$(uname -s)-$(uname -m)" -o /usr/local/bin/docker-compose

sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/docker-compose
docker-compose --version
docker-compose up -d


